{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act22side_level_act22side_04_end","storyGroup":"act22side","storySort":9,"storyDependence":"act22side_level_act22side_04_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"FC-4","storyName":"热灼梦","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"苇草祛除了深池士兵身上的法术后，得救的塞尔蒙与她谈起了自己对深池寄托的理想。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act22side/level_act22side_04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act22side_04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":7,"next":9,"characters":["拉芙希妮","父亲","爱布拉娜","塞尔蒙","苇草"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"$loneliness_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":11},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你害怕我的火吗？可你的火与我的是一样的，拉芙希妮。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":12},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"它会永远燃烧，想要去蒙住它的光焰，让它熄灭，是徒劳的。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":13},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"不用畏惧让人看到。为什么不让看到的人畏惧它呢？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":14},{"type":"subtitle","id":15},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":17},{"type":"Dialog","id":18},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":19},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"Character","id":21},{"type":"Background","image":"21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d","screenadapt":"showall","id":22},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.8","fadetime":"0","id":23},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":24},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":25},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":26},{"type":"Text","text":"我知道我的体内有一团火。只要去摸索就会感到灼痛，时间久了，痛觉甚至比我的想法先一步浮现。","id":27},{"type":"Text","text":"父母告诫我们，把这天生的火焰吞下去，藏起来，不要被任何人看见。","id":28},{"type":"Text","text":"但我知道，姐姐总是悄悄地烧掉自己不想要的东西，然后就能得到更好的。","id":29},{"type":"Text","text":"我是不是也可以？","id":30},{"type":"Dialog","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"爸爸，可以带我去书店吗？","id":32},{"type":"Dialog","id":33},{"type":"character","id":34},{"type":"Text","text":"那天早上，我想试着扮演她，用她的语气跟父母讲话。","id":35},{"type":"Text","text":"每一次她向父母提出要求的时候，父母都会像被火烫到一样，惊惶又怜爱地答应。","id":36},{"type":"Text","text":"我和她有着一样的相貌与声音，穿着一样的衣服，为什么我不能假装成她的样子？","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"我想看蒸汽骑士冒险故事的续集......因为，我不想被其他人问，为什么会有维多利亚人不喜欢看蒸汽骑士的故事。","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"父亲","text":"......明天吧，拉芙希妮。爸爸妈妈今天已经很累了。","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"爸爸......认出来我了？","id":40},{"type":"Dialog","id":41},{"type":"character","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"父亲","text":"当然，我怎么会分不清自己的两个女儿呢？","id":43},{"type":"Dialog","id":44},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":45},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"Character","id":47},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"showall","id":48},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":49},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":50},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":51},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":52},{"type":"Text","text":"那个雪夜过后我才明白，他们不答应我，是因为我想要的东西太小了。","id":53},{"type":"Text","text":"如果是她的话，是不会连一本新印的小说都要从父母那里求来的。","id":54},{"type":"Dialog","id":55},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":56},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":57},{"type":"Character","id":58},{"type":"Background","image":"21_G6_decisivebattlealley_n","screenadapt":"showall","id":59},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.8","fadetime":"0","id":60},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":61},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":62},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":63},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$bigbell","volume":"1","id":64},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":65},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$bigbell","volume":"1","id":66},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","delay":"0.2","id":67},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":68},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$bigbell","volume":"1","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":70},{"type":"Text","text":"我跟在她身后，拼命地奔跑。","id":71},{"type":"Text","text":"团聚的钟声响了，可是，家已经回不去了。","id":72},{"type":"Dialog","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"姐姐......我们，要去哪里？","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"......你想去哪里呢？","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"我，不知道......","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"既然哪里都不是家，那就随便敲开一扇门吧。","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"你只需要坦诚地告诉来开门的人，我们在这个节日的雪夜里无家可归。","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"无论多么冷漠的人，应该也是能对两个孩子生出同情心的。","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"去吧，拉芙希妮，别害怕。我在看着你呢。","id":80},{"type":"Dialog","id":81},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":82},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":83},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"1","id":84},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":85},{"type":"Text","text":"在冰冷的紫色火焰映照下，我颤抖着敲开了第一扇门。","id":86},{"type":"Text","text":"那是刚刚取走了我们仇人性命的火焰，我却好像知道，如果我做错了什么，它也会转头来杀死我。","id":87},{"type":"Dialog","id":88},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":90},{"type":"Character","id":91},{"type":"Background","image":"34_g6_noblelivingroom","screenadapt":"showall","id":92},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":93},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":94},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":95},{"type":"character","name":"avg_226_weed_1#2","fadetime":"0.7","id":96},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"——可是，老师他做错了什么？","id":98},{"type":"Dialog","id":99},{"type":"Character","id":100},{"type":"Text","text":"我听说，塔拉人的街区在上演一出戏剧，所以这样的大雪夜里，老师迟迟没有回家。","id":101},{"type":"Text","text":"姐姐领我在老师的书房里坐下。她没有直接回答我的问题，只是温和地注视着我。","id":102},{"type":"Text","text":"我知道，她对我很失望。我应该能够自己找到答案。","id":103},{"type":"Dialog","id":104},{"type":"character","name":"avg_226_weed_1#2","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"......他教我们，毁去无辜者的生活，激化塔拉人与维多利亚人的矛盾。","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"他还......谋害了落魄的政敌，就像，那些维多利亚人，害死我们的父母一样。","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"所以，取走他的性命......是该做的事情。","id":108},{"type":"Dialog","id":109},{"type":"Character","id":110},{"type":"Text","text":"姐姐总是能做出正确的事情，我却做不到。","id":111},{"type":"Text","text":"她把枪送给了我，可每一次握住那柄燃烧着火焰的长枪，我都在发抖。","id":112},{"type":"Text","text":"就像此时。","id":113},{"type":"Dialog","id":114},{"type":"character","name":"avg_226_weed_1#2","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"我说的......对吗？","id":116},{"type":"Dialog","id":117},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":118},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":119},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":120},{"type":"Character","id":121},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"showall","id":122},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":123},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"不，拉芙希妮。","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"死亡只不过会引他去往自己的理想。","id":127},{"type":"Dialog","id":128},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":130},{"type":"Character","id":131},{"type":"Background","id":132},{"type":"Image","image":"34_i04","xFrom":"100","yFrom":"-50","y":"100","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","fadetime":"2","id":133},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":134},{"type":"ImageTween","yTo":"0","duration":"3","block":"false","id":135},{"type":"Image","image":"34_i04","y":"0","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","fadetime":"3","id":136},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":137},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"$dignified_loop","volume":"0.4","id":138,"musicid":1},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"100","yFrom":"-50","xTo":"0","yTo":"-0","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"0.85","yScaleTo":"0.85","duration":"27","block":"false","id":139},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$firestorm","volume":"0.1","id":140},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":141},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":142},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"10","amount":"0","block":"false","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"他用阴谋与权术浇灌我们，剥下我们的自由与尊严，这当然可恨，但也只是可恨。","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"只是他的手段业已精熟，他的野心却太过狭隘，这才真正叫人惋惜。","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"他想要的，不过是掌控一个易碎的空想国度，令我们做他戴冠的傀儡。","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"我要握在手里的权力，却比他那狂人的空想，还要庞大得多。","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"——你呢，拉芙希妮？你想要什么呢？","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"你的血脉与教养让你高尚，这是好事，可你要是一无所求，我又该在身边留什么样的位置给你呢？","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"说吧，这可是雪夜里的愿望......多么大的野心，我都允许。","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"......","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉芙希妮","text":"......","id":152},{"type":"Dialog","id":153},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":154},{"type":"Text","text":"我没有回答。","id":155},{"type":"Text","text":"我只有小小的梦想，像壁炉里一团温暖的火。","id":156},{"type":"Text","text":"我不敢回答。","id":157},{"type":"Dialog","id":158},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"没关系，我的妹妹。既然你不知道自己的欲望在何处，那就先成为我吧。","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"爱布拉娜","text":"往后，你与我便都是“领袖”。","id":161},{"type":"Dialog","id":162},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":164},{"type":"image","id":165},{"type":"Character","id":166},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":167},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"showall","id":168},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":169},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":171},{"type":"Text","text":"那火焰注视着我，我成为了她的影子。","id":172},{"type":"Dialog","id":173},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":174},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":176},{"type":"Character","id":177},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_wild_a","screenadapt":"showall","id":178},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":179},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.4","id":180,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":181},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":182},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"哈......你一直跟着我？什么时候？","id":184,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"不，只是我从维恩那里听说，你在深池的死者队伍里，见到了自己的哥哥......","id":186,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我猜你会自己来这里。","id":188,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"这件事应该和你没关系。","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我这一路......都在寻找这些被法术操纵的死者。我希望他们获得平静。","id":192,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我也的确能做到。就像刚才你看到的那样。","id":193,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1","name2":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"......","id":195,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":196},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":197},{"type":"Text","text":"不再有士兵行军的脚步声，荒野变得沉默。","id":198},{"type":"Dialog","id":199},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"0.7","id":200},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":201},{"type":"Text","text":"她们谁也没说话。过了一会儿，塞尔蒙蹲下来，拍了拍面罩上的尘土，然后小心地盖在士兵的脸上。","id":202},{"type":"Dialog","id":203},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1","id":204},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"......那个多事的维恩，有没有跟你说过我第一次见到深池时的事情？","id":205,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"那会儿我们在城里，我跟我哥，心情好就去排队看看有没有酒馆需要临时侍应生，心情不好就用弹弓打维多利亚人的窗玻璃。","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"哈，其实我也不知道那些贵族是不是维多利亚人，我只知道把我们从农用地块上赶走的那个贵族是。","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"然后有一天，有个受伤倒在小巷子里的人用塔拉语叫住我，让我帮她送信。","id":210,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我们猜到了她的身份。我送了信，还给她找了个地方藏起来。","id":211,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#7$1","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我告诉她，在我心中这座城市最坏的维多利亚人，第一名要数那个颁布法令的小胡子贵族。","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"什么针对塔拉酒鬼的酒税啦，源石制品税啦，把没工作的塔拉人集中起来安置的法令啦，都是他在电视上说的。","id":214,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1","id":215},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"然后还有驻扎在矮街的军官，我眼睁睁看着他打死好几个人，只要多瞪他一眼，就会被他抓走。","id":216,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"他们鬼魂部队要找袭击目标，必须把这些人算上。","id":217,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"可她回答我，不对，深池的目标不是替塔拉人报复维多利亚人。","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我哥就告诉她，哪个贵族有最大的房子，哪个贵族的宴会最气派，哪个贵族的一间储物室就能武装一支部队，养活一个地块的农民。","id":219,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"她说，那就更不对了，深池也不是要抢劫维多利亚人来救济塔拉人。","id":220,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"她还说，只是杀死一些人，然后自己坐上他们的位置，不会让塔拉人的境况变得更好，只会把我们变成他们。","id":221,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"就像学习维多利亚的礼仪，模仿维多利亚人的口音，这样的塔拉人，也可以当上维多利亚的贵族......","id":222,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......那，深池想要什么，她告诉你们了吗？","id":224,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#2$1","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"哈，没有。但后来我哥想明白了，所以我们决定加入深池，按照他们留下的讯息去找他们。","id":226,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1","id":227},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我们离开了移动城市，前往邻近的聚落。","id":228,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"就在那条公路上，我突然想起来深池是怎么清理目击者的。","id":230,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我很害怕，怕到不得不逃跑了。","id":231,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我也不是恨每一个维多利亚人啊，我不恨的那些人，我还没准备好让他们流血啊。","id":232,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"但......那是不得不做的事。","id":234,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"我，不喜欢这么说。可是，深池是一支军队，军队面前只有战争。","id":235,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我知道，我当然知道。","id":237,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"理智上，我知道他们是正确的。","id":238,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"错在我做不到。","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"......为什么哥能做到的事我做不到？为什么他能那么坚定，我却要逃跑？","id":241,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#6$1","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"为什么他能忍受死亡，忍受死后仍在燃烧，我却连看着他变成这副模样都不能忍受？","id":243,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":245,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":246},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","focus":"-1","id":247},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":248},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"为什么她能从灰烬里站起来，我却只能躲在影子里哭泣？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":250},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"拉芙希妮，你想要的是什么？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":251},{"type":"subtitle","id":252},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":253},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":254},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......“我为你写下，我生命所知的爱与梦”......","id":256,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"“可在那燃烧的狂喜里，爱与梦都无处容身”......","id":257,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"啊？","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"你......不会在念诗吧？","id":260,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#6$1","id":261},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"真的？对我念诗？想显得自己有教养？","id":262,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":263},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"抱歉......我，不知道该怎么说。","id":264,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"鼓励别人、安慰别人的话，我可以讲很多......但那都不是我的。","id":265,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"哈......别念下去了......","id":267,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"......","id":268,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":269},{"type":"character","id":270},{"type":"Text","text":"塞尔蒙将脸埋在了双手之间。","id":271},{"type":"Text","text":"她的悲痛与那些不再言语的深池士兵一样，笼罩在深绿色的轮廓下。","id":272},{"type":"Text","text":"“我梦见......”他们低声说。","id":273},{"type":"Dialog","id":274},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1","id":275},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"好几年前，我们还在维多利亚人的庄园里干活儿的时候。","id":276,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"有一天，我哥劝我扔掉手里的事情，跟他一起溜出去玩。","id":277,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"......我们走了好长时间，走到了农用地块的边缘，望着下面的荒野。","id":279,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"看不到尽头的土地，土地上开满野花。我哥说，那就是塔拉。","id":280,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"他说了很多又蠢又自大的话，很大声地对着风唱歌。","id":281,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"他说维多利亚人夺走了我们的语言，所以我们有很多话想说却说不出，只能把爱和悲伤都藏在古老的民谣里。","id":282,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#2$1","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"他还说我们做了一件了不起的事，我们今天不给维多利亚人干活，这就是反抗了维多利亚人。","id":284,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"当时他可能真的很自豪，真的梦想着成为传说故事里的英雄......哈。","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我也一样。","id":287,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"......你留给他的火焰，很漂亮。就像那天我们看到的花。","id":288,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"可它不是真的花，只是......","id":290,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":291},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1","focus":"-1","id":292},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"“从我们的生到死，不过是眨眼一瞬。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":295},{"type":"subtitle","id":296},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":298},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1","id":299},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......甚至，你都没办法握住它。","id":300,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"没事，我不在乎。","id":302,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1","id":303},{"type":"multiline","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我早就知道他会死。我们去找深池的时候，连我都做好了自己会死的准备。","id":304},{"type":"multiline","name":"塞尔蒙","end":"true","text":"我......不在乎。","id":305},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"我也从来不信他能像自己吹嘘的一样，像我们的梦想一样，死得像个英雄。","id":306,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1","id":307},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"但是，苇草......我想要听句实话，你自己的实话。","id":308,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞尔蒙","text":"他到死还在追求的东西，那个......深池许诺的未来，是假的吗？","id":309,"figure":"avg_npc_724_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"苇草","text":"......","id":311,"figure":"avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":312},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":313},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":314},{"type":"Character","id":315},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"showall","id":316},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":317},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$firestorm","volume":"0.1","id":318},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":319},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":320},{"type":"Text","text":"黑夜下，一簇火焰从枪尖燃起。","id":321},{"type":"Text","text":"在火光的映照中，苇草看见，泪水终于流过她的脸庞。","id":322},{"type":"Dialog","id":323},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":324},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"Character","id":326},{"type":"Image","id":327}],"characters":["拉芙希妮","父亲","爱布拉娜","塞尔蒙","苇草"]}